review_blob: I was a little dissappointed with the Kells, as Im usually a big fan of anything Rogue puts out.  As expected, this was very similar to Harp, but a bit hoppier.  It had a slightly crisper, more American flavor profile.  It certainly did its job, but didnt blow me out of the water; it ends up tasting a bit thin and has a somewhat dry mouthfeel.
